block content
  main#content.bd-masthead(role='main')
    .container(data-animation='fadeIn')
      span.bd-booticon.outline B
      p.lead.animation-fast.animated.fadeInDown(data-animation='fadeIn')
        | Bootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS framework in the world for building responsive, mobile-first projects on the web.
      p.lead
        a.btn.btn-outline-inverse.btn-lg(href='/getting-started/download', onclick="ga('send', 'event', 'Jumbotron actions', 'Download', 'Download 4.0.0-alpha');") Download Bootstrap
      p.version Currently v4.0.0-alpha
          
  .bd-featurette
    .container
      h2.bd-featurette-title Easy to get started.
      p.lead
        | Quickly include Bootstrap's CSS and JS into any project. Use your favorite package manager, download the source, or use the Bootstrap CDN.
      .row
        .col-sm-6.m-b-lg
          h4 Managed dependencies
          p
            | Include Bootstrap's source Sass and JavaScript files via Bower, Composer, Meteor, or npm. Package managed installs don't include documentation, but do include our Gruntfile and readme.
          p
            a.btn.btn-bs.btn-outline(href='/getting-started/download/#package-managers') View install methods
        .col-sm-6.m-b-lg
          h4 Bootstrap CDN
          p
            | When you just need to include Bootstrap's compiled CSS and JS, use the Bootstrap CDN, free from the Max CDN folks.
          p.text-muted Not yet available, but hopefully soon!

